WEBVTT

01:39.550 --> 01:43.160
[Road to Success]

01:44.550 --> 01:47.720
[Episode 27]

01:56.789 --> 01:57.479
Hello.

01:57.950 --> 01:59.810
Is this Yuanyuan Tutoring Class?

02:01.840 --> 02:03.280
Here is a package for you.

02:05.920 --> 02:06.710
Thank you.

02:18.340 --> 02:21.820
[Congratulations to Hongjing No. 8 High School
Football Team on Advancing]

02:22.250 --> 02:23.050
[Motion-Sensing Game Console]
[Trip for Two]

02:23.070 --> 02:24.079
[Autographed Football Jersey]
[LEGO Set]

02:24.100 --> 02:25.280
[Prize Claim Hotline]

02:33.630 --> 02:36.280
PS5, 5,999 yuan?

02:33.710 --> 02:35.410
[Gift 1]

02:35.520 --> 02:37.810
[Gift 2]

02:36.280 --> 02:38.750
Road bike, 6,990.

02:37.810 --> 02:39.260
[Gift 3]

02:38.750 --> 02:40.960
Smartphone, 6,999.

02:39.329 --> 02:40.560
[Gift 4]

02:40.960 --> 02:44.560
Congratulations to Hongjing No. 8 High School
Football Team on advancing.

02:44.560 --> 02:45.360
Here.

02:47.079 --> 02:48.870
Ms. Lin is so generous.

02:48.870 --> 02:51.840
So we are supposed to pick one gift each?

02:51.840 --> 02:52.430
I want that one.

02:52.430 --> 02:53.630
Then I want the autographed jersey.

02:53.630 --> 02:54.079
Let me see.

02:54.079 --> 02:55.360
Wait.

02:55.360 --> 02:55.910
Why did Ms. Lin

02:55.910 --> 02:57.750
give us a new phone number?

02:57.870 --> 02:58.430
I don't think...

02:58.430 --> 03:00.800
it's Ms. Lin at all.

03:01.080 --> 03:03.280
Each of these gifts is over 5,000 yuan.

03:03.280 --> 03:05.610
Ms. Lin would never spend that much money.

03:05.630 --> 03:06.430
True.

03:07.310 --> 03:08.910
Coach, what do you think?

03:08.910 --> 03:10.210
Is it Ms. Lin?

03:11.000 --> 03:12.080
I hope so.

03:13.240 --> 03:14.840
But it doesn't look like her.

03:15.400 --> 03:16.800
Such an official tone.

03:17.210 --> 03:18.740
It's clearly not her style.

03:19.910 --> 03:21.640
Could it be the mystery person?

03:25.560 --> 03:27.620
We'll know if we make a call, won't we?

03:28.000 --> 03:28.840
Okay, hurry.

03:28.840 --> 03:29.520
The number. It's...

03:29.520 --> 03:30.360
I have a phone.

03:30.360 --> 03:31.150
Use this one.

03:40.360 --> 03:41.190
Hello.

03:41.190 --> 03:43.010
You've reached
the Prize Redemption Center.

03:43.010 --> 03:47.120
Congratulations to Hongjing No. 8 High School Football Team
on advancing.

03:47.120 --> 03:48.920
These are the available prizes.

03:49.800 --> 03:51.760
Press 1 to claim your prize.

03:52.030 --> 03:53.190
Press 2 to accept the new task:

03:53.190 --> 03:55.870
A Sky Full of Stars.

03:56.079 --> 03:58.690
The countdown begins now: 15 seconds.

03:58.960 --> 04:01.800
If you do not make a selection
within the allotted time,

04:01.800 --> 04:03.430
you will be deemed to have declined
all tasks.

04:03.430 --> 04:05.910
What? What does "A Sky Full of Stars"

04:05.910 --> 04:06.750
mean?

04:06.750 --> 04:08.310
Should I press 1 or 2 now?

04:08.310 --> 04:09.430
Fifteen seconds. Hurry.

04:09.430 --> 04:10.630
-Hang up.
-What are you doing?

04:10.630 --> 04:11.800
What are you doing, bro?

04:11.800 --> 04:12.870
If you keep hesitating,

04:12.870 --> 04:15.330
it will assume
you've already made a choice.

04:15.520 --> 04:17.399
This is actually
a multiple-choice question.

04:17.399 --> 04:18.519
Do we choose one

04:19.630 --> 04:20.510
or two?

04:23.090 --> 04:25.350
Why do I feel like two is Ms. Lin?

04:25.380 --> 04:26.260
Right.

04:26.390 --> 04:28.240
That "Xing" in her name means star.

04:28.240 --> 04:29.040
Right.

04:29.040 --> 04:30.480
And it's "Wanxing."

04:31.400 --> 04:33.400
Could he have news about Ms. Lin?

04:33.510 --> 04:34.190
-It's possible.
-It's possible.

04:34.190 --> 04:34.950
I think so.

04:35.530 --> 04:37.780
Captain, you make the choice.

04:43.430 --> 04:44.960
Although it's just a guess,

04:45.510 --> 04:47.570
I still want to choose the second one.

04:48.070 --> 04:49.190
Because I don't want to give up

04:49.190 --> 04:50.970
any clues to find Ms. Lin.

04:51.070 --> 04:52.390
I don't want to miss this chance either.

04:52.390 --> 04:52.950
-Yeah.
-Me too.

04:52.950 --> 04:54.390
We finally have a clue.

04:55.480 --> 04:57.940
Here, the phone is with me.
Make the call now.

05:03.430 --> 05:04.430
Put it on speaker.

05:06.070 --> 05:06.800
Hello.

05:06.800 --> 05:08.560
This is the prize redemption center.

05:08.560 --> 05:09.340
Press two.

05:11.070 --> 05:12.830
You have selected two.

05:12.830 --> 05:15.070
Next, please receive the fax.

05:15.070 --> 05:16.200
The fax?

05:16.220 --> 05:17.880
-Let's take a look.
-Let's go.

05:27.970 --> 05:28.670
[If I can stop one heart from breaking,]

05:28.690 --> 05:29.510
[I shall not live in vain.]

05:29.270 --> 05:30.390
What is this?

05:29.540 --> 05:30.010
[If I can ease one life the aching,]

05:30.040 --> 05:30.720
[or cool one pain,]

05:30.860 --> 05:32.240
Is it another puzzle?

05:32.240 --> 05:33.750
It's a poem?

05:33.750 --> 05:35.240
what does this mean?

05:33.890 --> 05:34.690
[Or help one fainting robin,]

05:34.710 --> 05:35.770
[Unto his nest again,]

05:35.240 --> 05:35.920
I don't know.

05:35.790 --> 05:37.040
[I shall not live in vain.]

05:35.920 --> 05:39.120
New mission: Save a lost star.

05:37.070 --> 05:40.620
[New mission: Save a lost star]

05:39.120 --> 05:40.360
Wanxing? Lin?

05:40.640 --> 05:42.530
[Bonus Clue]

05:40.800 --> 05:42.159
Is this Ms. Lin's email?

05:42.159 --> 05:42.750
An email?

05:42.790 --> 05:44.990
[Log in]

05:47.620 --> 05:50.920
[Inbox]

05:47.750 --> 05:50.280
Yongchuan Hengjiu Appointment Notice?

05:51.360 --> 05:51.920
Coach.

05:51.920 --> 05:53.120
Open it and let us see.

05:54.570 --> 05:56.350
[President's Office of
Yongchuan Hengjiu Football Club]

05:55.920 --> 05:57.750
Appointment Notice?

05:56.370 --> 05:57.430
[The Presidium—Appointment Notice]

05:57.860 --> 05:58.700
[Yongcheon Hengjiu Football Club
Co., Ltd.]

05:58.360 --> 06:01.240
Yongchuan Hengjiu Football Coach
Appointment Notice.

05:58.720 --> 06:00.360
[Notice Regarding
the Appointment of the New Head Coach]

06:00.460 --> 06:01.030
[Coach Liu Chuanguang
has been appointed as Head Coach]

06:01.060 --> 06:01.780
[of Yongchuan Hengjiu Club's first team.
This notice is hereby issued.]

06:01.240 --> 06:02.680
November 2nd?

06:03.270 --> 06:04.360
Liu Chuanguang?

06:05.750 --> 06:07.550
This was sent the day I left.

06:08.070 --> 06:09.480
Ms. Lin said

06:09.480 --> 06:11.600
it was a mystery person
who gave her an email,

06:11.600 --> 06:12.160
which was how she found out

06:12.160 --> 06:13.560
you didn't go to Hengjiu.

06:16.070 --> 06:17.580
Then this email must be from

06:17.580 --> 06:18.940
the mystery person.

06:23.470 --> 06:24.940
[Dear mystery person]

06:26.800 --> 06:28.410
Dear mystery person,

06:29.120 --> 06:31.160
I don't know how to address you.

06:31.830 --> 06:34.360
So I'll just call you the mystery person.

06:35.480 --> 06:36.800
I have a feeling

06:37.430 --> 06:38.630
that all along,

06:38.920 --> 06:40.310
the one
who made the football lending card,

06:40.310 --> 06:43.830
the crossword puzzles,
and provided this email

06:44.480 --> 06:45.940
should be the same person.

06:46.920 --> 06:50.920
And that person is you,
the mystery person.

06:57.720 --> 06:58.970
I can feel

06:59.550 --> 07:00.750
that you want me

07:00.780 --> 07:02.330
to step out of my cage,

07:02.740 --> 07:04.750
join the kids on the team,

07:05.390 --> 07:08.250
and lead them
to find the meaning of football again.

07:09.680 --> 07:11.280
I've wondered many times

07:11.670 --> 07:12.840
who you really are.

07:13.600 --> 07:15.000
But now I feel

07:15.770 --> 07:17.680
that this mysterious journey

07:18.070 --> 07:20.750
might slowly lead me to you.

07:21.560 --> 07:23.070
I don't need to rush.

07:25.360 --> 07:26.430
Perhaps

07:27.150 --> 07:29.350
you'll never log into this email again,

07:29.960 --> 07:32.710
but it once connected us.

07:33.830 --> 07:36.159
I think I'll use it

07:37.750 --> 07:39.950
to record the moments of the team and me.

07:44.800 --> 07:45.600
So,

07:45.600 --> 07:48.190
I'll start
by sharing something very happy.

07:48.390 --> 07:50.950
I ran really fast yesterday.

07:51.480 --> 07:52.680
I got Wang Fa back.

08:04.490 --> 08:06.270
[Crushing Defeat to Yongchuan Hengjiu]

08:06.760 --> 08:08.240
Dear mystery person,

08:08.660 --> 08:09.770
in today's match,

08:10.110 --> 08:12.030
we played against Yongchuan Hengjiu

08:12.030 --> 08:13.830
and suffered a crushing defeat.

08:13.950 --> 08:14.960
Before the match,

08:14.990 --> 08:17.280
Coach gave me a heads up.

08:17.950 --> 08:18.800
He said

08:18.800 --> 08:20.480
that we might lose this time.

08:21.510 --> 08:22.120
No.

08:22.750 --> 08:25.480
He meant that we couldn't win.

08:26.680 --> 08:29.460
But I always felt that no matter what,

08:29.630 --> 08:31.630
we should still have a chance to win.

08:32.240 --> 08:33.480
But actually,

08:34.120 --> 08:35.000
we didn't.

08:35.669 --> 08:38.080
Even though I was informed
of the outcome in advance,

08:36.210 --> 08:39.429
[Hongjing No. 8 High School
0-11 Yongchuan Hengjiu]

08:38.080 --> 08:40.080
when the failure actually arrived,

08:40.390 --> 08:41.720
I still felt terrible.

08:44.480 --> 08:46.030
When I close my eyes now,

08:46.630 --> 08:49.190
all I see is Chen Jianghe
falling on the pitch

08:49.480 --> 08:51.870
and the football flying into our goal.

08:52.720 --> 08:53.750
It turns out

08:53.920 --> 08:56.500
the gap between us and a professional team

08:56.690 --> 08:57.950
is this huge.

09:10.310 --> 09:11.140
But,

09:11.840 --> 09:12.880
does this mean

09:12.910 --> 09:15.600
we can never defeat a strong opponent?

09:19.190 --> 09:20.910
Actually, in my worldview,

09:21.260 --> 09:23.530
winning or losing in football
isn't that important.

09:23.530 --> 09:25.880
What matters is football itself.

09:26.550 --> 09:29.080
It's about whether you're happy
during the process,

09:29.080 --> 09:30.510
whether you've gained something,

09:30.510 --> 09:32.910
and whether you've found
the meaning of it.

09:35.510 --> 09:36.320
But...

09:37.270 --> 09:38.870
I found that once you fail,

09:39.440 --> 09:41.160
these so-called processes

09:41.310 --> 09:44.440
bring no happiness, gains, or meaning.

09:45.120 --> 09:48.470
They only bring pain.

09:51.150 --> 09:52.150
Before the match,

09:52.290 --> 09:53.890
Coach asked me to think about

09:54.080 --> 09:56.530
what football itself really is.

09:58.740 --> 10:01.840
Anyway,
he hasn't figured it out himself either.

10:02.240 --> 10:04.760
It's okay if I can't figure it out

10:04.780 --> 10:06.140
for now, right?

10:09.250 --> 10:10.630
But so far,

10:11.390 --> 10:11.790
I think

10:11.790 --> 10:14.200
the most charming aspect
of competitive sports

10:14.200 --> 10:15.290
is still about

10:15.550 --> 10:17.110
the weak defeating the strong,

10:17.110 --> 10:18.420
-turning impossible
-Hongjing No. 8 High!

10:18.420 --> 10:20.020
-into possible.
-Go! Go! Go!

10:21.680 --> 10:25.260
Carrying many unanswered questions,

10:25.440 --> 10:28.070
people pursue seemingly
impossible victories,

10:28.070 --> 10:31.470
running as hard as they can on the pitch.

10:43.480 --> 10:44.080
Coach,

10:44.870 --> 10:46.670
there's an unsent email in the drafts.

10:44.970 --> 10:52.610
[Drafts]

10:48.880 --> 10:49.790
What is it?

10:52.880 --> 10:55.930
[To Mr. Win]

10:53.710 --> 10:54.710
Mr. Win?

10:56.000 --> 10:58.640
Could it be a love letter to Coach?

10:58.750 --> 11:00.180
Open it. Open it.

11:00.240 --> 11:01.670
Coach.

11:01.750 --> 11:01.980
[To Mr. Win]

11:02.020 --> 11:03.110
[Inbox]

11:05.890 --> 11:08.250
[A Victory]

11:06.200 --> 11:07.660
This one should be for you.

11:10.070 --> 11:10.240
[A Victory]

11:11.130 --> 11:12.370
Dear mystery person,

11:12.910 --> 11:14.510
I believe you should know

11:14.510 --> 11:17.310
about the kids
defeating Lyujing International.

11:18.870 --> 11:21.750
Actually, my impression
of the Youth Super League

11:22.080 --> 11:22.720
is still based on

11:22.720 --> 11:25.320
their last match
against Ning'an Experimental School.

11:25.320 --> 11:27.150
Since they are all students,

11:27.150 --> 11:29.040
even though they were dominated
by their opponents,

11:29.040 --> 11:32.240
they were able to turn the tide
with Coach Wang's tactics.

11:32.720 --> 11:35.080
But this match was different.

11:35.750 --> 11:36.790
Lyujing was obviously

11:36.790 --> 11:38.560
a much stronger team.

11:38.580 --> 11:40.040
Wang Fa's absence

11:40.070 --> 11:41.870
put me under even more pressure.

11:42.400 --> 11:44.060
But I was very clear at the time

11:44.270 --> 11:45.550
that this match

11:45.750 --> 11:47.320
wasn't going to be a one-and-done.

11:47.320 --> 11:49.380
That was the real Youth Super League.

11:50.270 --> 11:52.090
Whether it was me or the kids,

11:52.670 --> 11:55.800
our state of mind
was completely different from before.

11:57.970 --> 11:59.830
Lyujing was really quite strong.

12:00.390 --> 12:01.380
But in the end,

12:01.500 --> 12:03.000
we still won.

12:06.960 --> 12:08.720
Cheese!

12:09.590 --> 12:10.510
The kids

12:10.510 --> 12:12.500
even hung up a banner at school,

12:12.530 --> 12:14.360
making it quite a big deal.

12:14.750 --> 12:15.720
It's a pity that

12:15.720 --> 12:18.770
no one around paid attention or cared.

12:18.870 --> 12:20.150
However, I know that

12:20.840 --> 12:24.320
this victory
is of great significance to them.

12:31.030 --> 12:33.090
Although few people paid attention,

12:33.630 --> 12:34.960
that was the first time I saw

12:34.960 --> 12:36.240
pride in their eyes.

12:37.070 --> 12:38.390
That pride

12:38.410 --> 12:41.070
might not be
the brightest star in the night sky,

12:41.160 --> 12:42.630
but it still shines.

12:44.360 --> 12:45.580
I believe

12:45.600 --> 12:47.380
they will go far.

12:48.030 --> 12:49.420
One day,

12:49.450 --> 12:51.510
everyone will see them in a new light.

12:57.970 --> 12:59.900
From the abandoned equipment room

13:00.030 --> 13:01.760
to the passionate green field,

13:02.130 --> 13:04.360
the epic comeback
of a group of underachievers

13:04.360 --> 13:05.510
begins right here.

13:06.260 --> 13:07.850
I am really happy.

13:09.390 --> 13:11.910
I believe you are too.

13:13.130 --> 13:15.020
[Wen Chengye's Journey to a New Beginning]

13:14.260 --> 13:16.620
This one is about Wen Chengye.

13:23.030 --> 13:23.860
[Wen Chengye's Journey to a New Beginning]

13:25.440 --> 13:26.750
Dear mystery person,

13:27.760 --> 13:29.890
today I'd like to share with you

13:29.910 --> 13:31.790
how I witnessed a gifted young boy,

13:31.790 --> 13:33.120
trapped at the bottom of a deep well,

13:33.120 --> 13:34.630
find a new beginning.

13:36.640 --> 13:39.680
Wen Chengye had
a deeply unhappy childhood.

13:40.390 --> 13:42.150
There were deep rifts

13:42.180 --> 13:43.640
between him and Fu Xinshu,

13:43.910 --> 13:45.570
and between him and football.

13:46.540 --> 13:47.780
This child

13:48.400 --> 13:50.640
has always been a special existence.

13:51.510 --> 13:52.720
When we first met,

13:53.390 --> 13:55.190
he was like a poisoned hedgehog,

13:55.770 --> 13:58.170
protecting his wounded heart with spines.

13:59.370 --> 14:00.400
Today,

14:00.790 --> 14:02.610
in our match against Xinpeng,

14:02.800 --> 14:04.320
I sent him an email.

14:05.070 --> 14:07.970
Deep down, I still hoped he'd come.

14:09.370 --> 14:10.880
I could feel

14:11.010 --> 14:13.140
-his passion for football
-You idiot.

14:13.150 --> 14:14.580
-and his sensitive
-A bunch of idiot.

14:14.580 --> 14:15.960
-psychological defenses
-Say it again!

14:15.960 --> 14:18.560
-pulling him in opposite directions.
-Qin Ao!

14:19.870 --> 14:22.160
I saw that every attempt
we made to get close to him

14:22.160 --> 14:23.890
triggered his defensiveness.

14:24.630 --> 14:26.830
But every time he used words and actions

14:26.910 --> 14:28.270
to hurt us,

14:28.750 --> 14:29.790
he also pulled out

14:29.790 --> 14:31.480
one of his own thorns.

14:32.750 --> 14:35.790
He chose this way
of hurting others and himself

14:36.270 --> 14:38.000
to get closer to us step by step,

14:38.670 --> 14:40.310
actually because

14:40.510 --> 14:42.470
he was afraid of losing again.

14:43.850 --> 14:45.070
-Friendship,
-Thank you.

14:45.070 --> 14:46.280
care,

14:46.300 --> 14:47.180
passion,

14:47.210 --> 14:48.050
and himself—

14:48.640 --> 14:50.580
these are all the things he longs for

14:50.580 --> 14:52.390
yet fears to lose.

14:55.200 --> 14:56.320
During the match,

14:56.650 --> 14:58.780
I showed him the video of our match.

14:59.560 --> 15:01.220
He saw his teammates,

15:01.250 --> 15:02.650
under the scorching sun,

15:02.650 --> 15:06.380
fighting with determination
and reckless passion for every ball.

15:07.440 --> 15:08.390
On the screen,

15:08.880 --> 15:10.960
he said to me in a hoarse voice,

15:11.450 --> 15:13.490
"I don't know if there is still time,

15:13.510 --> 15:14.930
but I'll still come.

15:14.960 --> 15:16.020
I definitely will.

15:16.520 --> 15:17.310
Wait for me.

15:17.330 --> 15:18.790
You guys must wait for me."

15:20.180 --> 15:21.230
I saw him

15:21.910 --> 15:23.680
running to the field

15:24.360 --> 15:25.550
and us.

15:26.200 --> 15:27.030
Wen Chengye.

15:28.860 --> 15:31.260
[Microphone on] [Speaker on]
[Camera off]

15:29.080 --> 15:31.420
I don't know if there is still time,

15:32.210 --> 15:33.640
but I'll still come.

15:34.480 --> 15:36.450
I definitely will. Wait for me.

15:41.550 --> 15:43.080
If he had made it,

15:43.400 --> 15:44.930
if he hadn't been stubborn,

15:45.150 --> 15:47.280
if he had seen his own heart earlier...

15:47.960 --> 15:49.590
He had countless regrets

15:49.630 --> 15:51.490
and countless impossible "ifs."

15:52.790 --> 15:55.320
But by the time
Wen Chengye ran onto the field,

15:55.390 --> 15:57.320
he was already a brand-new person.

15:58.600 --> 16:00.000
All the ifs,

16:00.670 --> 16:01.870
all the frustration,

16:02.480 --> 16:04.940
and all the tears he shed
with his teammates—

16:06.080 --> 16:09.870
in fact, they've been healing each other
all this time.

16:12.000 --> 16:13.200
I'm sorry, everyone.

16:19.080 --> 16:19.960
I'm sorry.

16:30.630 --> 16:31.910
Dear mystery person,

16:32.510 --> 16:33.820
thank you for witnessing

16:33.820 --> 16:35.080
Wen Chengye's rebirth

16:35.550 --> 16:37.240
and for watching these children

16:37.240 --> 16:37.680
bravely face their inner selves,

16:37.680 --> 16:39.510
step by step, alongside me.

16:40.550 --> 16:41.550
At this moment,

16:42.440 --> 16:43.670
I was healed too.

16:45.270 --> 16:49.320
I feel really happy.

17:03.960 --> 17:04.790
Well...

17:06.480 --> 17:08.589
This makes me want to cry.

17:10.030 --> 17:11.890
I didn't expect Ms. Lin

17:12.020 --> 17:13.490
to write all this down.

17:14.160 --> 17:14.920
Coach.

17:16.640 --> 17:18.200
Can you bring Ms. Lin back?

17:20.069 --> 17:20.680
Yes.

17:22.960 --> 17:25.160
Because her heart has always been here.

17:38.450 --> 17:39.310
[To Mr. Win]

17:43.150 --> 17:44.540
Good evening, Wang Fa.

17:46.640 --> 17:49.370
I've never done this before,

17:49.720 --> 17:51.390
so I feel a bit shy.

17:55.090 --> 17:56.110
First of all,

17:56.850 --> 17:59.310
thank you for your company
during this time,

17:59.640 --> 18:01.770
and for your guidance for the players.

18:03.230 --> 18:04.920
Perhaps to you, they are

18:05.680 --> 18:07.810
just passers-by you met along the way.

18:08.980 --> 18:11.780
You just casually rescued
some drowning kittens,

18:12.270 --> 18:14.870
picking them up
and letting them dry in the sun.

18:15.440 --> 18:16.680
But you know what?

18:17.120 --> 18:18.640
For a kitten,

18:19.110 --> 18:20.590
basking in the sunlight

18:21.030 --> 18:22.900
is the happiest

18:23.150 --> 18:24.750
and safest thing in its life.

18:26.430 --> 18:27.870
Thank you so much.

18:37.040 --> 18:39.190
Is that a bit too fake?

18:40.310 --> 18:42.510
Although these are my true feelings...

18:46.140 --> 18:48.010
They aren't completely sincere.

18:54.070 --> 18:56.640
Rationally speaking,
I can't tell you what I truly want to say

18:56.640 --> 18:58.260
from the bottom of my heart.

18:59.310 --> 19:00.480
But anyway,

19:00.480 --> 19:01.830
I'll cut this part out,

19:02.480 --> 19:03.680
so it doesn't matter.

19:05.720 --> 19:06.400
Wang Fa.

19:08.030 --> 19:09.690
Knowing that you are leaving,

19:12.240 --> 19:13.900
I have a very strange feeling.

19:16.200 --> 19:17.800
It's a sense of loss, I think.

19:19.510 --> 19:20.750
It should be.

19:23.680 --> 19:25.240
You are the most interesting guy

19:25.240 --> 19:26.610
I've ever met.

19:28.590 --> 19:30.200
Every day with you

19:30.200 --> 19:32.430
is lively and relaxing.

19:33.920 --> 19:37.750
Although you seem like someone
with a lot of stories,

19:40.460 --> 19:42.220
I also have many secrets.

19:44.590 --> 19:45.640
These days,

19:45.640 --> 19:47.270
with you and the students here,

19:47.270 --> 19:49.730
every day is fulfilling and busy,

19:51.160 --> 19:53.240
so busy that I can temporarily forget

19:54.080 --> 19:55.840
those unanswered questions.

20:02.550 --> 20:04.160
There was a time before

20:05.740 --> 20:07.790
when I couldn't sleep all night.

20:09.630 --> 20:11.830
But as long as I thought of you upstairs,

20:13.150 --> 20:15.770
coming up with
some new drink for tomorrow,

20:17.030 --> 20:19.030
I looked forward to a new day.

20:24.510 --> 20:28.030
It feels really good
to have someone's company.

20:31.310 --> 20:32.960
But now you are leaving.

20:34.270 --> 20:36.130
The upstairs will be empty again,

20:38.680 --> 20:40.160
and I will be alone again.

20:44.440 --> 20:45.880
I know this is selfish,

20:47.390 --> 20:49.150
but I still want to ask you—

20:52.860 --> 20:54.450
could you stay

20:56.400 --> 20:57.350
for me

20:58.640 --> 20:59.770
and keep me company,

21:01.590 --> 21:02.240
please?

21:08.400 --> 21:09.350
I will.

21:10.880 --> 21:11.790
Lin Wanxing.

21:31.640 --> 21:32.970
Why did you call me here?

21:37.350 --> 21:38.610
You didn't call me here

21:38.890 --> 21:41.370
to show off

21:41.400 --> 21:43.130
your doll collection, did you?

21:44.710 --> 21:45.990
I need your help.

21:46.440 --> 21:47.300
I'm listening.

21:48.880 --> 21:51.610
I've been waiting around in Hanling
for too long.

21:52.270 --> 21:54.270
I've decided to take a step forward.

21:57.880 --> 21:58.480
Okay.

22:03.230 --> 22:08.470
[Hanling]

22:20.170 --> 22:21.460
♪ Time's passing by ♪

22:22.110 --> 22:24.000
♪ Nothing remains ♪

22:25.090 --> 22:27.660
♪ All the dreamers awake alone ♪

22:25.120 --> 22:29.260
[Pet Sale]

22:28.360 --> 22:30.060
♪ Shadows above ♪

22:30.850 --> 22:32.560
♪ Rain falls around ♪

22:30.940 --> 22:33.650
[Can you stay for us?]

22:33.140 --> 22:33.970
♪ In your arms ♪

22:33.810 --> 22:36.410
Sorry.
One sparkling iced Americano, please.

22:34.770 --> 22:36.240
♪ We become one ♪

22:36.480 --> 22:37.330
Thank you.

22:37.020 --> 22:38.680
♪ Through day and night ♪

22:37.370 --> 22:38.970
He already ordered for you.

22:39.200 --> 22:41.400
Thank you.

22:39.420 --> 22:41.450
♪ I can see you ♪

22:42.500 --> 22:44.740
♪ In my eyes ♪

22:44.990 --> 22:45.610
Here.

22:45.600 --> 22:47.070
♪ Just hold me tight ♪

22:46.920 --> 22:48.320
I'm done putting them up on my side.
How about you?

22:47.910 --> 22:53.120
♪ Look into my soul so deeply ♪

22:49.200 --> 22:50.400
Two more places to go.

22:52.910 --> 22:55.220
Are you sure you want to be so cryptic?

22:53.860 --> 22:55.610
♪ Rainbow sunlight ♪

22:54.830 --> 22:57.160
[Can you stay for us?]

22:55.240 --> 22:56.880
You're not gonna write something
sentimental?

22:56.460 --> 22:57.600
♪ Painful tears are gone ♪

22:58.510 --> 22:59.550
♪ Wonderful days ♪

23:00.530 --> 23:01.970
♪ Are so close to me ♪

23:02.930 --> 23:04.100
♪ Memories fly ♪

23:04.000 --> 23:05.160
I'm taking the umbrella.

23:05.000 --> 23:06.250
♪ Leave them all behind ♪

23:05.680 --> 23:06.440
Wait, if you take the umbrella,

23:06.440 --> 23:07.350
what am I supposed to...

23:07.260 --> 23:12.860
♪ Just take my hand and stay with me ♪

23:10.030 --> 23:11.160
I'll go with you.

23:11.160 --> 23:12.760
I don't have an umbrella now.

23:21.500 --> 23:26.570
[Busy Dog]

23:26.640 --> 23:27.960
Little puppy.

23:30.920 --> 23:33.830
Is this your little braid? Hello. Hello.

23:36.590 --> 23:37.310
Sit.

23:38.070 --> 23:38.790
Sit.

23:44.640 --> 23:45.510
Here.

23:45.680 --> 23:47.000
What is this?

23:49.200 --> 23:52.000
Do you like it? Call me Sister.

24:00.180 --> 24:01.820
Chubby little guy.

24:01.920 --> 24:03.680
You really are a chubby dog.

24:08.720 --> 24:09.680
Is it good?

24:18.750 --> 24:19.920
Bye-bye.

24:24.340 --> 24:26.370
[Can you stay for us?]

24:33.280 --> 24:34.620
[Pet Sale]

24:34.660 --> 24:37.990
[Can you stay for us?]

24:53.890 --> 24:55.160
[Can you stay for us?]

25:00.780 --> 25:04.950
[Can you stay for us?]

25:07.770 --> 25:09.570
I know this is very selfish,

25:11.410 --> 25:13.560
but I still want to ask you—

25:15.170 --> 25:16.440
for me, could you...

25:16.470 --> 25:18.310
for us, could you...

25:18.440 --> 25:19.070
Stay?

25:19.100 --> 25:20.130
Stay?

25:20.680 --> 25:21.770
Wang Fa,

25:22.080 --> 25:24.770
you watched the video in the email?

25:37.010 --> 25:41.750
[163 Email]

25:41.780 --> 25:43.320
[Waiting for a Star Forever]

25:45.170 --> 25:45.730
[Waiting for a Star Forever]

25:47.640 --> 25:50.310
This is a movie ticket
waiting to be redeemed.

25:50.400 --> 25:52.220
Starlight Cinema at MixC.

25:52.690 --> 25:53.820
It's valid forever.

26:12.530 --> 26:15.580
[Scan Here]

26:20.330 --> 26:21.530
[Service unavailable.
Please try again later.]

26:25.860 --> 26:26.690
Hello.

26:26.950 --> 26:27.670
Hello.

26:27.920 --> 26:28.920
I can't scan the QR code

26:28.920 --> 26:30.480
with the machine to get my ticket.

26:30.480 --> 26:32.010
Okay, please wait a moment.

26:35.930 --> 26:36.180
[Loading]

26:36.180 --> 26:36.920
[Redemption Successful]
[Waiting for a Star Forever]

26:38.810 --> 26:40.240
Oh, it's Theater 9.

26:40.270 --> 26:41.200
This theater

26:41.200 --> 26:43.070
has been booked long-term.

26:47.240 --> 26:48.660
[Redemption Successful]
[Waiting for a Star Forever]

26:59.380 --> 27:00.210
Thank you.

27:18.160 --> 27:18.600
[Starlight Cinema, MixC]

27:19.100 --> 27:19.380
["Waiting for a Star Forever"
Voucher Redeemed]

27:19.410 --> 27:19.660
[March 1st, 2026, Starlight Cinema, MixC]

27:19.720 --> 27:20.030
[Theater 9 IMAX Ticket, 17:40]

27:27.890 --> 27:29.430
[Little Savage Tribe]

27:30.960 --> 27:33.310
Ms. Lin redeemed her movie ticket.

27:45.920 --> 27:46.880
Ms. Lin!

27:46.880 --> 27:48.160
I want to share our life with you

27:48.160 --> 27:49.790
and show you the results
of our vegetable planting.

27:49.790 --> 27:50.640
I drew this at the time.

27:50.640 --> 27:51.730
These are the bell peppers I grew.

27:51.730 --> 27:52.970
Don't they look nice?

27:53.000 --> 27:54.720
This was planted by Boss.

27:54.750 --> 27:55.940
The coolest Ao.

27:55.970 --> 27:56.880
Boss,

27:56.880 --> 27:59.140
why don't you introduce this vegetable?

28:00.730 --> 28:02.620
Fine, you don't know how.

28:03.640 --> 28:05.680
Please add more spice.

28:05.680 --> 28:07.640
Who says I don't know?

28:07.640 --> 28:09.840
It's called... Shanghaiqing, right?

28:10.110 --> 28:11.410
That's right!

28:11.590 --> 28:12.160
Ms. Lin,

28:12.160 --> 28:13.640
these are the scallions I grew.

28:13.640 --> 28:14.480
Ms. Lin,

28:14.480 --> 28:15.790
the peppers you planted are right here.

28:15.790 --> 28:16.510
They are really delicious.

28:16.510 --> 28:18.160
You will definitely love them.

28:18.160 --> 28:19.160
Not bad.

28:19.160 --> 28:20.880
This is baby bok choy.

28:20.880 --> 28:21.680
This is the most important one,

28:21.680 --> 28:22.510
Ms. Lin.

28:22.510 --> 28:24.310
This is that pepper I grew.

28:24.310 --> 28:25.880
-Look. I planted a lot.
-What pepper?

28:25.880 --> 28:27.680
There are so many.

28:27.680 --> 28:28.880
This is the best vegetable I've grown.

28:28.880 --> 28:30.200
You, Boss.

28:30.920 --> 28:32.590
These are loofahs.

28:33.640 --> 28:34.510
Ms. Lin, this loofah is rotten.

28:34.510 --> 28:35.640
I'm cutting it off.

28:35.920 --> 28:36.880
Let's go.

28:36.880 --> 28:37.880
Next one.

28:38.350 --> 28:39.920
These are water spinach and stuff.

28:39.920 --> 28:41.640
And these are eggplants.

28:41.640 --> 28:42.790
Why is it so wilted?

28:42.790 --> 28:43.510
Don't ask me.

28:43.510 --> 28:44.030
Ask...

28:44.030 --> 28:44.920
I'll ask you.

28:44.920 --> 28:46.110
The manager was asking me...

28:46.110 --> 28:47.110
Chengye,

28:47.110 --> 28:48.440
why is this eggplant so wilted?

28:48.440 --> 28:50.500
The person who didn't water it knows.

28:51.200 --> 28:52.880
Who didn't water it?

28:52.880 --> 28:53.830
-Come on.
-Let's go.

28:53.830 --> 28:55.160
Why are we going down?

28:55.550 --> 28:58.280
Boss is pretending to be
a good student over here.

28:58.550 --> 28:59.980
Doing homework?

29:00.020 --> 29:00.350
Let's go.

29:00.350 --> 29:01.270
Let's go take a look.

29:01.270 --> 29:04.330
I don't know if he's actually doing it
or just faking it.

29:05.270 --> 29:06.160
I feel like...

29:06.180 --> 29:07.310
Ms. Lin.

29:07.310 --> 29:09.830
I bet they are playing on their phones.

29:09.830 --> 29:10.680
Because I just saw them

29:10.680 --> 29:12.880
hiding their phones under their books.

29:13.070 --> 29:14.550
Let's go down and catch them red-handed.

29:14.550 --> 29:15.590
I'll show you.

29:15.590 --> 29:16.310
It's fine.

29:16.310 --> 29:17.480
Let me show you.

29:18.110 --> 29:19.790
Who is working so hard?

29:19.790 --> 29:21.100
You two,

29:21.350 --> 29:23.160
stop pretending.

29:27.270 --> 29:28.600
We made this ourselves.

29:28.640 --> 29:30.120
Ms. Lin!

29:30.150 --> 29:31.790
Ms. Lin!

29:32.310 --> 29:34.070
This is the vegetable we grew ourselves.

29:34.070 --> 29:36.330
This is the vegetable we grew ourselves.

29:38.590 --> 29:39.790
So many peppers.

29:39.790 --> 29:40.950
Coach. Coach.

29:40.980 --> 29:42.610
Coach, why are you sleeping here again?

29:42.610 --> 29:44.010
Come here.

29:44.200 --> 29:44.830
Stop sleeping.

29:44.830 --> 29:45.960
Time to eat noodles.

29:47.110 --> 29:49.000
Coach really loves to sleep.

29:49.030 --> 29:50.400
Let me serve you some, Coach.

29:50.400 --> 29:50.880
Oh, right, Coach.

29:50.880 --> 29:52.880
We're recording a video for Ms. Lin.

29:52.880 --> 29:54.560
Do you want to say something?

29:55.640 --> 29:56.790
Ms. Lin,

29:57.440 --> 29:58.720
we miss you so much.

30:06.910 --> 30:07.820
Ms. Lin,

30:07.840 --> 30:09.520
we won the playoff match.

30:10.000 --> 30:12.110
We all believe in you.

30:12.610 --> 30:15.230
You sound like a villain.

30:16.310 --> 30:17.510
Ms. Lin,

30:17.510 --> 30:18.960
we will always support you.

30:18.960 --> 30:20.510
This will always be your safe haven.

30:20.510 --> 30:21.310
We love you.

30:21.310 --> 30:22.510
-Yes.
-Yes.

30:22.590 --> 30:23.880
We'll always be here waiting for you,

30:23.880 --> 30:25.430
waiting to eat noodles with you.

30:25.430 --> 30:26.800
With lots of chili...

30:26.830 --> 30:28.160
And no cilantro.

30:29.910 --> 30:31.020
Ms. Lin,

30:31.040 --> 30:32.640
we're gonna go eat noodles now.

30:32.640 --> 30:34.070
Bye-bye, Ms. Lin.

30:34.110 --> 30:35.980
Bye-bye!

30:36.000 --> 30:37.510
-Bye-bye.
-Bye-bye.

30:56.200 --> 30:57.160
Ms. Lin.

30:58.720 --> 30:59.650
Long time no see.

31:01.840 --> 31:03.800
I'm recording this video for you

31:04.680 --> 31:05.960
because after you left,

31:05.960 --> 31:08.640
we received a strange package
and a strange fax.

31:10.430 --> 31:12.800
We also found out
the real reason you left.

31:17.750 --> 31:19.950
When we first heard those stories,

31:21.740 --> 31:22.870
we were all very sad.

31:25.690 --> 31:27.100
But I didn't know

31:28.000 --> 31:30.340
♪ Night slips through my fingers ♪

31:28.270 --> 31:29.430
how to comfort you.

31:30.960 --> 31:35.080
♪ Embracing the coldness of wakefulness ♪

31:32.320 --> 31:34.320
I couldn't even say,

31:35.580 --> 31:37.540
♪ Whispering my thoughts alone ♪

31:38.280 --> 31:43.100
♪ Saying goodbye to the evening breeze
I chanced upon ♪

31:39.560 --> 31:40.820
"It's all in the past."

31:43.270 --> 31:44.070
Wanxing.

31:43.770 --> 31:46.570
♪ Staying with the jasmine blossoms
until late spring ♪

31:45.240 --> 31:47.090
You have always been
a beacon for the kids.

31:47.090 --> 31:50.400
♪ Watching their elegance fade,
their fragrance disappear ♪

31:48.260 --> 31:49.500
When they were lost,

31:49.550 --> 31:50.950
you gave them direction.

31:51.480 --> 31:54.240
♪ I once dreamed of something beautiful ♪

31:52.070 --> 31:53.920
We recorded these stories

31:54.310 --> 31:56.030
not just because we miss you.

31:55.160 --> 31:59.280
♪ And I accept that
regrets may grow wild ♪

31:57.110 --> 31:58.640
We also want to tell you that

31:59.480 --> 32:01.940
even if you still don't want to come back,

31:59.960 --> 32:02.410
♪ Look, beneath the sunlight ♪

32:02.960 --> 32:07.130
♪ In the dancing specks of dust ♪

32:03.040 --> 32:04.370
we will all wait for you.

32:06.330 --> 32:07.620
Our beacons

32:07.650 --> 32:10.450
♪ I'm grateful I never lost my sincerity ♪

32:08.400 --> 32:10.000
are lighting the way for you.

32:11.090 --> 32:14.770
♪ Or my gift for happiness ♪

32:13.360 --> 32:14.560
I remember

32:15.860 --> 32:18.190
when I first decided to leave the UK,

32:16.320 --> 32:18.360
♪ Sharing my warmth with a passing rain ♪

32:19.210 --> 32:22.920
♪ Quietly feeling its journey ♪

32:19.700 --> 32:20.900
I woke up one day

32:21.720 --> 32:24.580
and somehow wandered
to St. Mary's Stadium,

32:24.060 --> 32:26.480
♪ Like a firefly vanishing in an instant ♪

32:25.440 --> 32:27.150
where I bought a ticket to watch a game.

32:27.150 --> 32:30.860
♪ Still beautiful in its entirety ♪

32:29.790 --> 32:31.030
That game didn't change

32:31.030 --> 32:32.880
my decision to leave the team,

32:31.720 --> 32:34.250
♪ There's no need to seek a final answer ♪

32:33.810 --> 32:34.570
but

32:35.180 --> 32:38.950
♪ Let the ending remain with
questions unanswered ♪

32:36.000 --> 32:37.790
I still remember the joy

32:37.790 --> 32:39.750
that victory brought me to this day.

32:39.750 --> 32:42.320
♪ No need to prove it with promises ♪

32:41.920 --> 32:44.030
So I hope that, like me,

32:43.300 --> 32:47.060
♪ The dusk when we once vowed
to stay together ♪

32:44.680 --> 32:46.280
when you suddenly look back,

32:47.200 --> 32:48.680
you'll find that
they're all beautiful memories.

32:47.910 --> 32:50.340
♪ No need to cling to forever ♪

32:50.850 --> 32:54.250
♪ Allow parting to happen quietly ♪

32:51.310 --> 32:52.200
Don't worry.

32:53.510 --> 32:54.910
The kids are doing great.

32:55.520 --> 32:58.120
♪ The inner voice hidden in the origami ♪

32:55.590 --> 32:57.590
They are stronger than we imagined.

32:59.480 --> 33:04.880
♪ Each scratch and line
is proof of beauty ♪

33:01.200 --> 33:02.270
Ms. Lin,

33:03.640 --> 33:06.000
you really taught them well.

33:11.720 --> 33:12.640
Lin Wanxing,

33:15.790 --> 33:16.920
we all miss you.

33:18.480 --> 33:19.860
Ivory misses you too.

33:21.200 --> 33:22.510
The guy at the supermarket said

33:22.510 --> 33:24.440
a lot of new mystery boxes arrived.

33:25.270 --> 33:26.510
I bought them all.

33:27.640 --> 33:28.720
When you come back,

33:29.750 --> 33:31.210
we can open them together.

33:31.340 --> 33:31.970
Okay?

34:13.150 --> 34:18.860
♪ Every experience has its meaning ♪

34:19.590 --> 34:24.389
♪ Scene by scene, they come together
to form who I am ♪

34:26.060 --> 34:31.210
♪ Even the wounds
that leave behind their marks ♪

34:32.190 --> 34:37.360
♪ Have taught me how to heal myself ♪

34:36.420 --> 34:37.060
You...

34:38.210 --> 34:44.170
♪ The love I have given,
the love I have received ♪

34:44.820 --> 34:50.590
♪ Every one of them gives me the strength
not to fear being hurt ♪

34:51.270 --> 34:56.880
♪ Let my tears be carried away,
back into the ocean ♪

34:57.730 --> 35:02.970
♪ And blown toward flowers
blooming far away ♪

35:03.820 --> 35:09.570
♪ The love I have given,
the love I have received ♪

35:10.430 --> 35:16.160
♪ Every one of them gives me the strength
not to fear being hurt ♪

35:16.880 --> 35:22.650
♪ Let my tears be carried away,
back into the ocean ♪

35:23.340 --> 35:28.720
♪ And blown toward flowers
blooming far away ♪

35:29.770 --> 35:35.380
♪ I fill the blank spaces of life
with colors ♪

35:35.440 --> 35:36.840
I'm so happy

35:35.960 --> 35:41.790
♪ My dreams are not afraid to awaken;
they continue to exist ♪

35:37.550 --> 35:40.080
that you redeemed
this movie ticket voucher.

35:42.480 --> 35:48.450
♪ I go beyond the dark clouds
and feel the haze disperse ♪

35:44.550 --> 35:45.320
Don't worry.

35:46.420 --> 35:47.970
I was the only one

35:49.140 --> 35:54.840
♪ Let me understand myself more clearly ♪

35:49.250 --> 35:51.250
who watched the video in your email.

35:56.670 --> 36:00.780
♪ Take away my reflection ♪

36:01.260 --> 36:03.460
Cheers!

36:11.310 --> 36:13.340
As the face of the team,

36:13.640 --> 36:15.100
I'd like to say a few words.

36:16.230 --> 36:17.150
Seriously? No respect?

36:17.150 --> 36:18.510
Am I not handsome?

36:19.900 --> 36:20.900
You are.

36:21.010 --> 36:22.740
Face of the team, go ahead.

36:23.670 --> 36:24.480
First,

36:24.670 --> 36:27.440
let's warmly welcome back Ms. Lin!

36:27.440 --> 36:29.440
Welcome!

36:32.430 --> 36:34.300
Secondly, I can testify

36:34.330 --> 36:36.770
that while Ms. Lin was away,

36:36.800 --> 36:38.770
Coach has behaved very well,

36:39.000 --> 36:40.190
devoting all his attention

36:40.190 --> 36:41.830
to Ms. Lin,

36:41.880 --> 36:44.190
with no sign of fooling around.

36:45.880 --> 36:46.880
I can testify too.

36:46.880 --> 36:48.510
-I can testify too.
-Me too.

36:48.510 --> 36:49.830
Well, thank you guys.

36:50.590 --> 36:51.400
So,

36:51.400 --> 36:52.630
the conclusion is—

36:53.110 --> 36:56.030
we approve of this marriage!

36:56.030 --> 36:57.400
-Yes!
-Yes!

37:02.320 --> 37:04.360
Lastly, we all agreed

37:04.380 --> 37:06.860
that the best welcome-back gift
for Ms. Lin

37:09.030 --> 37:11.320
would be a victory in the next game.

37:11.340 --> 37:14.300
We will fight to the end!

37:14.330 --> 37:18.040
Hongjing No. 8 High
will make it to the finals!

37:19.460 --> 37:21.150
Ms. Lin, say a few words.

37:29.540 --> 37:30.580
Thank you all.

37:32.670 --> 37:34.670
I also want to apologize to you again

37:35.710 --> 37:37.280
for my cowardice.

37:38.710 --> 37:39.920
No need for that at all.

37:39.920 --> 37:41.320
-Yeah.
-Exactly.

37:45.630 --> 37:47.630
When I was at Yongchuan University,

37:48.400 --> 37:50.320
I did experience something bad.

37:51.920 --> 37:53.190
I was framed.

37:55.230 --> 37:58.360
I tried to argue
with the people who framed me,

38:00.420 --> 38:03.150
but I ended up hurting
the person I loved the most.

38:13.720 --> 38:14.760
At that time,

38:16.220 --> 38:17.700
I was really sad.

38:23.890 --> 38:26.240
But when things fell apart this time,

38:26.870 --> 38:28.540
although I was also sad,

38:29.630 --> 38:32.020
I never thought about giving up on myself.

38:33.670 --> 38:34.510
I think

38:37.040 --> 38:38.700
it must be because of you guys.

38:41.890 --> 38:43.520
It is because of you guys

38:44.730 --> 38:46.480
that I feel

38:47.150 --> 38:48.550
that in this world,

38:50.470 --> 38:52.450
I'm no longer alone.

39:09.660 --> 39:11.250
Thank you so much.

39:13.750 --> 39:14.940
Ms. Lin,

39:15.690 --> 39:17.330
you are so mushy.

39:18.580 --> 39:20.450
I'm getting goosebumps.

39:21.050 --> 39:23.110
You two are so perfect for each other.

39:23.130 --> 39:24.660
Both masters of mushiness.

39:30.560 --> 39:31.560
Well...

39:35.120 --> 39:36.440
Today is a good day

39:36.470 --> 39:38.070
to set off confetti cannons!

39:41.320 --> 39:42.190
Ms. Lin,

39:42.190 --> 39:43.480
we love you!

39:43.480 --> 39:45.180
Love you, Ms. Lin!

39:45.670 --> 39:47.630
Ms. Lin, we love you!

40:00.670 --> 40:01.800
Coach, bye.

40:02.400 --> 40:03.190
Okay.

40:03.400 --> 40:04.670
Bye-bye, Ms. Lin.

40:04.670 --> 40:05.980
-Bye-bye.
-Bye-bye, Ms. Lin.

40:05.980 --> 40:07.030
Bye-bye.

40:07.030 --> 40:08.440
Be safe on the way.

40:20.150 --> 40:21.590
Emily's poem?

40:20.220 --> 40:20.840
[If I can stop one heart from breaking,]

40:20.860 --> 40:21.440
[I shall not live in vain.]

40:22.760 --> 40:23.840
Why is it here?

40:24.130 --> 40:24.930
Same as usual.

40:25.380 --> 40:27.510
It's a puzzle from the mystery person.

40:27.840 --> 40:29.290
Between expensive gifts

40:28.910 --> 40:29.530
[If I can stop one heart from breaking,]

40:29.440 --> 40:30.960
and a task with clues about you,

40:29.560 --> 40:29.970
[I shall not live in vain.]

40:30.000 --> 40:30.570
[If I can ease one life the aching,]

40:30.590 --> 40:31.110
[or cool one pain,]

40:31.140 --> 40:31.610
[Or help one fainting robin,]

40:31.640 --> 40:32.700
[Unto his nest again,]

40:31.810 --> 40:33.290
they asked the boys to make a choice.

40:32.720 --> 40:33.560
[I shall not live in vain.]

40:33.620 --> 40:34.770
[New mission: Save a lost star]

40:34.740 --> 40:35.900
Everyone chose the latter.

40:34.790 --> 40:35.730
[Bonus Clue]

40:41.460 --> 40:42.340
What's wrong?

40:43.230 --> 40:44.750
The mystery person...

40:46.470 --> 40:47.360
I think...

40:49.000 --> 40:50.630
I have an idea now.

41:03.230 --> 41:06.070
Don't you usually jog or walk here?

41:07.280 --> 41:08.510
When you were away,

41:09.070 --> 41:11.480
I saw your bike parked here
looking lonely,

41:12.190 --> 41:13.400
so I rode my bike over.

41:14.190 --> 41:14.960
Lonely?

41:16.400 --> 41:18.000
A bit stupid, I know.

41:19.920 --> 41:21.760
Not stupid. Thank you.

41:22.550 --> 41:27.680
[Yuanyuan Tutoring Class]

41:24.550 --> 41:26.110
Let's ride back together.

41:49.400 --> 41:50.760
Ivory.

41:50.760 --> 41:52.030
I heard that when I was away,

41:52.030 --> 41:54.360
you refused to let anyone trim your nails.

41:57.440 --> 41:58.670
I'm glad you're back.

41:59.320 --> 42:01.850
Otherwise,
I wouldn't know what to do with it.

42:02.710 --> 42:03.440
Come here.

42:11.880 --> 42:12.740
Are you hungry?

42:12.980 --> 42:15.100
I'm not. I just had hot pot.

42:15.150 --> 42:17.480
Then... should I help you unpack?

42:20.880 --> 42:21.720
Wang Fa,

42:22.210 --> 42:23.430
don't be so tense.

42:23.700 --> 42:24.880
I won't leave again.

42:27.510 --> 42:29.110
If you really want to comfort me,

42:29.110 --> 42:30.920
make me some cocktails.

42:30.920 --> 42:33.250
I've been longing for them
for a long time.

42:35.930 --> 42:36.610
Okay.

42:54.400 --> 42:55.200
You know what?

42:57.340 --> 42:58.780
After you left that day,

43:00.280 --> 43:02.010
I looked for you in many places.

43:03.590 --> 43:05.000
Finally, on the rooftop

43:05.000 --> 43:06.230
where we saved Ivory,

43:07.400 --> 43:08.730
I stayed for a long time.

43:10.840 --> 43:13.880
I thought about everything
you've been through

43:15.230 --> 43:16.800
and connected the dots.

43:20.590 --> 43:21.360
I'm sorry.

43:25.190 --> 43:26.800
That was when I realized

43:27.650 --> 43:28.910
how much this distrust

43:30.230 --> 43:31.630
must have hurt you.

43:31.630 --> 43:32.510
Wang Fa.

43:34.710 --> 43:36.030
It's all in the past.

43:43.000 --> 43:46.030
Besides, words are cheap.

43:46.760 --> 43:48.960
I need to see your actions in the future.

43:51.790 --> 43:54.050
♪ Two souls aligned ♪

43:55.660 --> 43:57.780
♪ In silent gravity ♪

43:59.820 --> 44:02.020
♪ Heal my heart ♪

44:00.040 --> 44:03.180
After seeing the posters
you guys put up that day,

44:02.560 --> 44:05.180
♪ With every part of you ♪

44:03.210 --> 44:04.740
I hesitated for a long time.

44:06.360 --> 44:08.670
The real reason I made up my mind...

44:07.750 --> 44:09.740
♪ Our words flow ♪

44:10.030 --> 44:11.280
Do you know what it is?

44:11.220 --> 44:13.220
♪ A gentle stream ♪

44:14.800 --> 44:15.760
I realized

44:15.530 --> 44:17.710
♪ They glow like fireflies ♪

44:16.800 --> 44:18.070
I could clearly remember

44:18.070 --> 44:19.840
the email account and password,

44:18.360 --> 44:20.880
♪ Inside a silken dream ♪

44:20.880 --> 44:22.920
as well as every name in it.

44:23.100 --> 44:29.000
♪ We talk the cool night, breeze away ♪

44:29.480 --> 44:30.360
Tomorrow...

44:30.920 --> 44:32.540
♪ We trace the roads ♪

44:32.470 --> 44:34.000
I want to go back to the school.

44:33.320 --> 44:36.430
♪ That never see an end ♪

44:35.590 --> 44:37.030
I won't run away anymore.

44:38.230 --> 44:39.920
This time, I must stand up

44:39.110 --> 44:42.520
♪ We softly calm the hidden doubt ♪

44:41.360 --> 44:42.490
and face everything

44:43.310 --> 44:47.920
♪ Seen in each other's eyes ♪

44:48.580 --> 44:52.550
♪ And wake the warmth inside ♪

44:54.500 --> 44:57.060
♪ Life begins alone ♪

44:57.610 --> 45:00.520
♪ A road we walk alone ♪

45:02.420 --> 45:04.640
♪ Until fate brings warmth ♪

45:05.240 --> 45:08.700
♪ To light our way back home ♪

45:10.780 --> 45:12.480
♪ True love is not just ♪
